Notes:

Comes in a thick sealable polysleeve with “Music On Vinyl” sticker on it, with poly-lined inner sleeve.

All writers except for Larry Muggerud are credited with their respective surnames on the back cover and with a combination of the first letter of the first name and the surname on the labels. Larry Muggerud is credited consistently as “Muggs” on back and as “L. Muggerud” on the center labels.
